OSMM — Open Systems Makerspace Manager
Copyright © 2026 OSMM-HQ and OSMM contributors.

Required Notice: Copyright OSMM-HQ (https://github.com/OSMM-HQ)

OSMM is a self-hostable, multi-tenant inventory and 3D-printing manager built for
makerspace communities — so a community can see what tools exist, who borrowed
what, what is available, and how 3D-printing work moves from request to
completion, without spreadsheets or guesswork.

